Story time ✨ Thought I was just vibing with life.
Turns out, I was unknowingly enrolled in a full-time course called:
“Crisis, Clarity & Character Development.”

From hospital visits and heartbreaks to therapy sessions and dream journaling, the universe really said:
“Character arc? Complete makeover.”

Now?
I’m not bouncing back—I’m bouncing forward.
With grace, grit, and just a little delulu magic.

If you're in your 'WTF is this?' phase—trust me, you're not behind. You're becoming.
Tag your soul sister, your journaling buddy, or anyone currently negotiating with the universe.
Let's rewrite our glow-up stories—one mildly panicked page at a time.

#HealingInProgress #DesiGlowUp
